      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been reliably maintained. The exterior still holds a great shine, though there are some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster. It runs smoothly and is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
