    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, currently held in pristine, showroom-level condition. Meticulously preserved and showing no signs of wear, this unit represents the absolute pinnacle of its class. The exterior retains its original luster, while the interior remains in an untouched state, reflecting a standard of care that is rarely achieved. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the individual who demands nothing less than mechanical and aesthetic perfection. Documentation of its rigorous maintenance history is available for review by serious parties.",
      "price": 48500.0,
