    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'showroom condition.' This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, retaining its deep, mirror-like factory finish with zero rock chips or swirls. The interior is equally pristine, featuring supple, untreated leather that still carries the original factory aroma; there are no signs of wear on the bolsters, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a complete, documented service history with every scheduled maintenance performed ahead of time at the dealership. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assists, functions flawlessly. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning collector who demands perfection. Non-smoker, no pets, and never seen a rainy day.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
