      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that defies its tenure. This specimen showcases a showroom-level aesthetic, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior environment that remains in pristine, original state. Meticulously preserved and mechanically superior, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands nothing short of perfection. Every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our rigorous criteria for automotive excellence.",
