    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? You\u2019ve found it! I have taken absolute pride in keeping this beauty in flawless shape\u2014it\u2019s seriously pristine inside and out. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It\u2019s been my absolute baby, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. You won't find one better cared for than this. Come see it for yourself!",
