      "description": "Offering an investment-grade BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This specimen is equipped with a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Technical highlights include a fully documented VANOS system overhaul, proactive rear subframe reinforcement, and pristine individual throttle bodies for instantaneous response. The suspension geometry remains true to factory tolerances, providing the legendary tactile feedback these chassis are known for. With zero mechanical deficiencies and a flawless exterior, this is a collector-quality example for the discerning driver.",
